title: MKM: Not Much Pushback on Lyft Valuation
text: Investors aren't showing much concern about the $23-billion valuation for ride-hailing company Lyft Inc.’s initial public offering as the company continues on a roadshow leading up to the IPO, MKM Partners said this week.

title: CobbleCord creates custom streaming bundles for users
text: CobbleCord CEO and founder Virginia Juliano discusses the free website that helps users navigate and find the best streaming plans for themselves, based on what they want to watch and how much they want to pay.
